00:02:29.251 --> 00:02:32.880
They make such a loud noise.

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:38.731
What's amazing is you know when you have wind gusts and straight line winds, it's just blowing at surface level.

00:02:38.731 --> 00:02:49.389
But whenever you hear a tornado turning up in the clouds and it's getting ready to come down, you can hear it up there.

00:02:49.389 --> 00:02:52.520
